=head1 DESCRIPTION

For a multi-location container fleet, describes the progress of a
deployment across all fleet locations.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 DeploymentStatus => Str

The status of fleet deployment activity in the location.

=over

=item *

C<IN_PROGRESS> -- The deployment is in progress.

=item *

C<IMPAIRED> -- The deployment failed and the fleet has some impaired
containers.

=item *

C<COMPLETE> -- The deployment has completed successfully.

=item *

C<ROLLBACK_IN_PROGRESS> -- The deployment failed and rollback has been
initiated.

=item *

C<ROLLBACK_IN_COMPLETE> -- The deployment failed and rollback has been
completed.

=item *

C<CANCELLED> -- The deployment was cancelled.

=back




